♪ That said too much ♪

847
01:16:17,390 --> 01:16:20,220
♪ To me any more ♪

848
01:16:26,400 --> 01:16:30,070
♪ There was a block, a snack ♪

849
01:16:30,230 --> 01:16:34,030
♪ Can't you change away ♪

850
01:16:34,200 --> 01:16:36,030
♪ Between us and you ♪

851
01:16:36,200 --> 01:16:38,370
♪ There's still ♪

852
01:16:38,530 --> 01:16:44,710
♪ Save us from yourself ♪

853
01:16:51,590 --> 01:16:55,170
♪ Come on girl ♪

854
01:16:55,340 --> 01:16:59,680
♪ It's a plastic knife ♪

855
01:16:59,850 --> 01:17:02,060
♪ And you'll look ♪

856
01:17:02,220 --> 01:17:09,900
♪ Nothing like you
did last night ♪

857
01:17:16,360 --> 01:17:20,160
♪ Come on, girl ♪

858
01:17:20,330 --> 01:17:24,120
♪ You'll be my dear ♪

859
01:17:24,290 --> 01:17:28,170
♪ My waterflower ♪

860
01:17:28,330 --> 01:17:33,380
♪ Whenever you are ♪

861
01:17:56,650 --> 01:18:00,660
♪ We want to discuss ♪

862
01:18:00,820 --> 01:18:09,160
♪ The after news within ♪

